  "title": "The CSO Toolkit Handbook: One contract, three languages — reproducible analytics in R, Python, and Stata",
  "description": "<p>The CSO Toolkit Handbook is the cross-language guide to the <code>cso-toolkit</code> contract: one IO + API contract, one producer / reviewer mode contract, and three idiomatic implementations in R, Python, and Stata. It documents how UNICEF Chief Statistician Office analytics are made reproducible and scalable across sectors and projects.</p><p>This Zenodo record archives the whole <code>cso-toolkit</code> repository. The handbook prose is licensed CC BY 4.0; the toolkit source code under <code>r/</code>, <code>python/</code>, and <code>stata/</code> is licensed MIT.</p>",
